       The shields weaked only for a moment, but quickly re-gained 
stabibility and went back to 100% strength. The EMP canon targeted 
Destructer, Galvatron, and the others sending 15 seeking blasts after them.
       Tarantulas watched them as the Autoguns shot at the jets over head. He 
turned to Klash who activated two side missles turrets. mounted behinde the 
shields, and ordred 5 missles to each enemy. The missles locked onto the 
spicific spraks and ran thier course of destruction.

--part1_68.c58a575.27cad5b9_boundary
